  "prompt": "League of Legends: What are the strengths and weaknesses of Brand?",
  "response": "Here's a breakdown of Brand's strengths and weaknesses in League of Legends:\n\nStrengths:\n1. High burst damage\n2. Strong area of effect (AOE) damage\n3. Good wave clear\n4. Excellent poke potential\n5. Strong crowd control with his passive stun\n6. Can punish grouped enemies\n7. Good in teamfights\n\nWeaknesses:\n1. Low mobility\n2. No escape mechanisms\n3. Vulnerable to engage champions\n4. Squishy/low health\n5. Relies heavily on landing skillshots\n6. Mana-intensive\n7. Can be shut down by champions with high mobility\n8. Vulnerable to ganks\n9. Falls off in late game if unable to get ahead\n\nOptimal roles:\n- Mid lane\n- Support\n- Occasional mid-lane mage\n\nTypical build focuses on:\n- Ability power\n- Magic penetration\n- Cooldown reduction\n- Health for survivability\n\nOverall, Brand excels at dealing massive magical damage and controlling teamfights with his AOE abilities, but requires careful positioning due to his vulnerability.",
